---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  theme="about"
  description="Structural biologist at the MRC Laboratory of Molecular Biology."
>
  <section class="container hero hero-top hero-wide">
    <div class="hero-primary">
      <h1>Sami Chaaban, PhD</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Investigator Scientist at the MRC Laboratory of Molecular Biology in Cambridge.
      </p>
      <p class="meta">
        I am a molecular and structural biologist with a broad background in studying
        the architecture and mechanisms of protein assemblies using biochemistry,
        cryo-electron microscopy, and fluorescence microscopy.
      </p>
      <p class="meta">
        My research spans from elucidating the structural basis of cytoskeletal
        function to developing software tools that streamline computational workflows.
      </p>
      <img
        class="headshot"
        src="/images/headshot.jpg"
        alt="Sami Chaaban"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/research/">Explore research</a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/cv/">View CV</a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Get in touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container focus-stack">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Microtubule motors</h3>
      <p class="meta">Architecture, adaptor binding, and regulation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Cryo-EM + Single Molecule</h3>
      <p class="meta">Structural and biophysical interrogation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Microtubule dynamics</h3>
      <p class="meta">Polymerization and non-canonical structures.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Computational tools</h3>
      <p class="meta">Pipelines that streamline microscopy analysis workflows.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-top {
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .hero-wide {
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
  }

  .hero-primary {
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .hero-primary h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
  }

  .hero-primary .lead {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  .hero-primary .meta {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .headshot {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 2;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }


  .focus-stack {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.6rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }


  .focus-stack .card {
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .focus-stack {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .focus-stack {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .focus-stack .card {
      aspect-ratio: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
